<div class="inner-container">
  <div class="card card-left">
    <div class="card-block">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <%= image_tag 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/chazona-portfolio-bucket/uploads/assets/images/chazona.png', width: 200, class: "profile-image d-block mx-auto", alt: "profile image" %>
          <div class="row">
            <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="progress">
                  <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped" role="progressbar" style="width:<%= skill.percent_utilized %>%;" aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100">
                    <span class="progress-label"><%= skill.title %></span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-8">
          <p>My name is Chazona Baum, and I am a self-taught full-stack developer with diverse experiences in industries ranging from food service to veterinary medicine to insurance.</p>

          <p>My love of code sprang from my love of language. Where some see confusing symbols, I see an elegant form of communication and expression, and a way for people to extend their capabilities and accomplish the previously impossible.</p>
          
          <p>I intend to utilize my customer-centric background and technical skills to build a career in advocacy and developer relations.</p>
          
          <p>To see what I'm doing now, check out my <%= link_to '#100DaysOfCode Log', 'https://hundred-days.herokuapp.com/logs' %>.</p>

          <p>
            <button 
              class="btn btn-primary mb-3" 
              type="button" 
              data-toggle="collapse" 
              data-target="#experience" 
              area-expanded="false" 
              aria-controls="experience"
            >
              Experience
            </button>

            <button 
              class="btn btn-primary mb-3" 
              type="button" 
              data-toggle="collapse" 
              data-target="#education" 
              area-expanded="false" 
              aria-controls="education"
            >
              Education
            </button>

            <button 
              class="btn btn-primary mb-3" 
              type="button" 
              data-toggle="collapse" 
              data-target="#featuredIn" 
              area-expanded="false" 
              aria-controls="featuredIn"
            >
              Featured In
            </button>
            <button 
              class="btn btn-primary mb-3" 
              type="button" 
              data-toggle="collapse" 
              data-target="#codingActivity" 
              area-expanded="false" 
              aria-controls="codingActivity"
            >
              Activity
            </button>
            <button 
              class="btn btn-primary mb-3" 
              type="button" 
              data-toggle="collapse" 
              data-target="#codingLanguages" 
              area-expanded="false" 
              aria-controls="codingLanguages"
            >
              Languages
            </button>
            <button 
              class="btn btn-primary mb-3" 
              type="button" 
              data-toggle="collapse" 
              data-target="#resume" 
              area-expanded="false" 
              aria-controls="resume"
            >
              Resume
            </button>
          </p>
          <div class="collapse" id="experience">
            <div class="card card-block">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-2">
                  <%= image_tag 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/chazona-portfolio-bucket/uploads/assets/images/logo_white_background_square.jpg', class: "img-fluid", alt: "Midlothian Code logo" %>
                </div>
                <div class="col-10">
                  <strong>Organizer/Web Developer</strong> - Lead the creation, growth and events of local code meetup Midlothian Code, as well as developing <%= link_to 'its website', 'https://midlothiancode.com' %>.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-2">
                  <%= image_tag 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/chazona-portfolio-bucket/uploads/assets/images/freecodecamp.png', class: "img-fluid", alt: "freeCodeCamp logo" %>
                </div>
                <div class="col-10">
                  Currently utilizing freeCodeCamp's computer software engineering program and working toward a full stack web development certification.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="collapse" id="featuredIn">
            <div class="card card-block">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-2">
                  <%= image_tag 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/chazona-portfolio-bucket/uploads/assets/images/devlogo.png', class: "img-fluid", alt: "The Practical Dev logo" %>
                </div>
                <div class="col-10">
                  Featured on the front page of <%= link_to 'The Practical Dev', 'https://dev.to' %> as well as <%= link_to '@ThePracticalDev', 'https://twitter.com/ThePracticalDev' %> Twitter account for a <%= link_to 'blog post on web development without a computer', 'https://dev.to/chznbaum/roughing-it-dev-style-coding-without-a-computer' %>.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-2">
                  <%= image_tag 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/chazona-portfolio-bucket/uploads/assets/images/codepenlogo.png', class: "img-fluid", alt: "CodePen logo" %>
                </div>
                <div class="col-10">
                  Featured in the <%= link_to 'CodePen Spark', 'https://codepen.io/spark/16' %> for my custom-CSS profile page.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="collapse" id="codingActivity">
            <div class="card card-block card-wakatime">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-12">
                  <figure><embed src="https://wakatime.com/share/@chznbaum/1aac19c3-ff53-447f-b840-d3a98a5a425e.svg"></embed></figure>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="collapse" id="codingLanguages">
            <div class="card card-block card-wakatime">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-12">
                  <figure><embed src="https://wakatime.com/share/@chznbaum/666ca127-6668-4d0f-85ce-b45614caced9.svg"></embed></figure>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="collapse" id="resume">
            <div class="card card-block card-wakatime">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-12">
                  <%= render 'shared/resume' %>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
